    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the chips are almost done, pat the <strong>basa fillets</strong> dry with kitchen paper and cut each fillet in half on a diagonal</p><p>Sprinkle both sides of the<strong> basa</strong> with <strong>flour</strong> until fully coated, then tap off any excess</p><p>Dip the<strong> floured basa</strong> into the <strong>batter</strong> and turn it several times until fully coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
